The paper involves the use of machine learning techniques (Monte Carlo Tree Search, image classifiers, Convolutional Neural Networks) to create a collaborative drawing environment between humans and machines. Therefore, it is likely to belong to the sub-categories of Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition (cs.CV), Graphics (cs.GR), Human-Computer Interaction (cs.HC), and Machine Learning (cs.LG).
